That's a good .gitignore but add these missing ones we talked about:
gitignore# Local environments
venv/
.env

# Data (We want the code, not the heavy files)
data/raw/
data/warehouse/
*.csv
*.parquet
*.xlsx

# Databases
*.duckdb

# Spark/Docker temp files
.ipynb_checkpoints
.DS_Store

# Logs
logs/
*.log
boot_logs.txt

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# dbt
dbt_project/target/
dbt_project/dbt_packages/
dbt_project/logs/